Design document created at `docs/design/automation-selected-text-saving.md` (16KB).

Covers 8 automation enhancements:
1. **AI-powered category prediction** — two-tier heuristic + AI `classifyText()` service
2. **One-click save from toolbar** — auto-categorize + save in 1 click with undo toast
3. **Background save** — double-tap / `Cmd+Shift+S` keyboard shortcut for instant save
4. **Inline mini save panel** — compact panel with auto-filled category/topic, replaces full popup
5. **Smart context menu** — auto-save as first item, 8-item sub-menu as fallback
6. **Session-based selection buffer** — accumulate selections, batch save all at once
7. **Smart de-duplication** — text-hash checking across stores to prevent re-saving
8. **Learning from user corrections** — tracks overrides, adjusts heuristic weights locally

Each section includes exact file paths, implementation patterns, and before/after behavior comparisons.
